[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and care-pathway instantiation, integration-layer maintenance and operational-state ingestion, coordination-event detection, engagement scheduling, channel entry, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading, conversation handling with care-pathway-grounded responses and action-confirmation, output safety screening, and escalation routing with care-team-and-coordinator reporting. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (integration-layer breadth as architectural primitive, care-pathway-as-code with care-management-leadership ownership, cross-system reconciliation, action-confirmation discipline for patient-initiated actions, and care-pathway-deviation severity classification).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CARE-PATHWAY INSTANTIATION ───────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolled by care team or program]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team places patient on a care pathway, or       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient self-enrolls into a coordination program     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-pathway template selected (per primary care     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      journey: oncology pathway per cancer type, transplant│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway per organ, advanced HF pathway, post-acute   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway, palliative pathway, complex-pediatric, etc.)│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care pathway instantiated with patient-specific      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      values: milestones, required referrals, monitoring   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      schedule, care-team roster, applicable protocols     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care pathway signed by clinical team                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team contact-routing graph instantiated         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient consents to assistant participation          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed care pathway record; coordination       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    enrollment record; longitudinal-store initialization]  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INTEGRATION LAYER + OPERATIONAL STATE ─────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational system integrations]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduling system (appointments across providers)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-management system                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - EHR for orders, results, encounters, problem list,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      medications, allergies, care plans, care teams       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prior-authorization tracking                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prescription / pharmacy systems                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Home-health-agency visit tracking                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Durable-medical-equipment tracking                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Financial-assistance / charity-care tracking         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management-platform records                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - HIE / cross-institutional exchange (where available) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational-state ingestion]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull (scheduled refresh) and push (event-driven)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ingestion patterns                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - FHIR-native ingestion where available                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured staleness tracking per data source        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reconciliation across sources                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational state store]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-patient integrated coordination picture          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open-coordination-items list (referrals to schedule, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      results to follow up on, prior auths to track,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      home-health visits to confirm, financial-assistance  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      to complete, etc.)                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Upcoming care-pathway milestones                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent operational events                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team roster with contact-routing                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-system discrepancies surfaced for review       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── COORDINATION-EVENT DETECTION ──────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Event detection from integration layer]                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral placed but not yet scheduled (after N days) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment scheduled (informational)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment near (proactive prep reminder)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment missed (no-show event)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pending order not yet completed                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Result returned (informational, with care-team       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      gating: some results are not patient-facing until    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the provider has reviewed them)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prior auth submitted, approved, denied, or pending   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (with thresholds for "stuck")                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prescription filled or not filled                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Home-health visit scheduled, completed, missed       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-pathway milestone approaching                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-pathway milestone missed (deviation)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-system discrepancy detected                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Transition-of-care event (discharge, transfer)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Severity and routing classification]                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-event-type severity per care pathway             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-facing engagement vs. care-team alert vs.    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      both                                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Deduplication and rate-limiting                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: coordination events to engagement scheduler    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    or to escalation pathway]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENGAGEMENT SCHEDULING ─────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Scheduled engagement sources]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-pathway-driven schedule (post-discharge         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      check-in, pre-procedure prep, post-procedure         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      check-in, milestone-approaching reminder)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination-event-triggered engagement              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-requested engagement                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Engagement-policy enforcement]                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Maximum daily engagement count                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Quiet hours per patient preference                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Channel preferences                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement-fatigue mitigation                        │
