[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── AUDIT, LOG, AND CONTINUOUS IMPROVEMENT ────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Durable conversation record]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User utterances                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated assistant responses                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care-pathway version                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active integration-layer version                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Action proposals and patient confirmations           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-decision-record journal]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Durable, separately-governed record of coordination  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      events: messages drafted and sent, actions confirmed │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and executed, escalations triggered, deviations      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      flagged                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to HIPAA's six-year minimum, state-  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      specific medical-record retention, institutional     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      operational-record retention                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination-coverage metrics (referrals tracked,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    541[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointments tracked, etc.)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination-completion metrics (referrals          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      completed, prior auths approved, missed milestones)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-facing engagement and attrition metrics      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Action-confirmation rates                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    546[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team alert volume and response                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    547[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled coordination-quality review]                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reviewers (care managers, care-coordination          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      operations, clinical leadership) tag failure modes:  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      out-of-scope, integration-stale, contact-routing-    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      error, action-mis-proposal, care-pathway-deviation-  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      missed, citation-gap, tone-failure                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-pathway and contact-routing revisions driven by │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      review findings                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: audit trail, telemetry, learning signals,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    care-pathway-revision proposals]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
